        <name>conn_mgr_all_if_up</name>
        <param>
          <type><ref refid="stdbool_8h_1abb452686968e48b67397da5f97445f5b" kindref="member">bool</ref></type>
          <declname>skip_ignored</declname>
        </param>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Convenience function that takes all available ifaces into the admin-up state. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Essentially a wrapper for <ref refid="group__net__if_1ga02644cc623fc7a8878c17d54984e4210" kindref="member">net_if_up</ref>.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>skip_ignored</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>- If true, only affect ifaces that aren&apos;t ignored by conn_mgr. Otherwise, affect all ifaces. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>0 if all net_if_up calls returned 0, otherwise the first nonzero value returned by a net_if_up call. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
